  a'_{r1} & \cdots & a'_{rs} & \cdots & a'_{rn} \\
\vdots & \ddots & \vdots & \ddots & \vdots \\
  a_{n1} & \cdots & a_{ns} & \cdots & a_{nn}
\end{vmatrix}$.
Similarly:
Then $\begin{vmatrix}
