296846431478121989235766506376027360743.text:
A pair of simultaneous linear equations of the form:
{{begin-eqn}}
{{eqn | l = a x + b y
      | r = c
}}
{{eqn | l = d x + e y
      | r = f
}}
{{end-eqn}}
where $a e \ne b d$, has as its only solution:
{{begin-eqn}}
{{eqn | l = x
      | r = \frac {c e - b f} {a e - b d}
}}
{{eqn | l = y
      | r = \frac {a f - c d} {a e - b d}
}}
{{end-eqn}}

